2024-05-24 <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1442152045/vector/path-route-icon-distance-symbol.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=2ilIa1pWHJp550B31t__1NPc0CHpouutgdxt7QO4EJg=" class="static-icon">28 km <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS_EkMEkMAdgDcE0W6nELzmmMrqHToRcoS8eA&s" class="static-icon">1429 m <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.freepik.com/512/13063/13063145.png" class="static-icon"><span>4:47:40</span>
        <a href="https://www.strava.com/activities/11487681160" class="icon-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/strava-2.svg" class="icon"></a></div>

<br>

<div class="description-text">First some rain and mud and slippery climbs but it got better by the end. The plan was to continue to Bayerischzell but I cut it short to be sure I wouldn’t miss the last train back.

⛰️ Hammerstein (1,278 m) • ⛰️ Zellerhorn (1,360 m) • ⛰️ Jagerwand (1,396 m) • ⛰️ Zellerwand (1,415 m) • ⛰️ Hochries (1,569 m) • ⛰️ Karkopf (1,496 m) • ⛰️ Pölcher Schneid (1,390 m) | 🌐 summitbag.com</div>

